# 🏁 F1 Strategy Bot

**AI-powered race engineer in your browser.**  
Simulate race strategies. Optimize pit stops. Visualize tire degradation.  
Because sometimes the pit wall *needs a little help*. 😉

---

## 🚦 Current Features

✅ Tire degradation chart  
✅ Pit stop windows visualization  
✅ Live race summary card  
✅ Loading spinner for pro UX  
✅ Modular JS structure → ready to scale  
✅ Mercedes-AMG inspired UI aesthetic  

---

## 🏎️ Stack

- **HTML** → structured interface  
- **CSS** → Mercedes-AMG styled UI  
- **JavaScript (modular)** → core logic  
    - `strategy.js` → main controller  
    - `charts.js` → Chart.js visualizations  
    - `summary.js` → live race summary  
- **Chart.js** → dynamic graphs  
- **Live Server (VS Code)** → dev server for local testing  

---

## ⚙️ Running Locally

1️⃣ Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/RaubCC/f1-strategy-bot.git
cd f1-strategy-bot
